    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and optimized by dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the preferred Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically sound, it has undergone critical subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure structural and valvetrain longevity. The suspension retains its telepathic feedback with refreshed bushings and dampers. While displaying minor patina consistent with its 'good' designation, the longitudinal rigidity and high-revving internals remain uncompromised. A purist\u2019s spec for those prioritizing mechanical integrity and analog engagement.",
