    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained Graphite Metallic sedan that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though it shows some honest character with minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, barely noticeable ding on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of black leather and brushed aluminum; while the driver\u2019s seat shows light softening on the side bolster, the upholstery remains supple and free of tears or stains. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has been serviced religiously at scheduled intervals, with a recent comprehensive inspection, fresh synthetic oil, and new brake pads all around. The tires are in great shape with plenty of tread remaining. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and has been a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that still feels tight and responsive on the road. This is a solid, reliable vehicle for someone who appreciates a car that has been cared for properly and is ready for its next chapter.",
